<template>
  <n-loading-bar-provider>
    <n-message-provider>
      <n-notification-provider>
        <n-dialog-provider>
          <e404 />
          <home />
        </n-dialog-provider>
      </n-notification-provider>
    </n-message-provider>
  </n-loading-bar-provider>
</template>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from "vue";
import E404 from "./views/404.vue";
import Home from "./views/home.vue";
import { darkTheme } from "naive-ui";

export default defineComponent({
  components: {
    E404,
    Home
  },
  setup() {
    return {
      darkTheme,
    };
  }
});
</script>
